You need to Install Django2.0.3 refer Django2.0.3 repository for installations
open command propmt
mkdir Django
cd Django
django-admin startproject djangocrud
cd djangocrud
django-admin startapp myapp
open your djangocrud project in your visual stdudio code editor
use CTRL+~ for open terminal and run below command to run the project
python3 manage.py runserver
close the terminal to migrate the database configuration and run the below commands
python3 manage.py makemigrations
python3 manage.py migrate
now run the project using below command
python3 manage.py runserver
check in your browser: 127.0.0.1:8000/show 
or localhost:8000/show
......................
